Flow - PHP Framework that aims to be quite impressive, to say the least.
========================================================================
Original Author:
	Brian Foster <bdfoster (at) endigotech (dot) com>
Contributors:
	Tim Juravich (via the book "CouchDB and PHP Web Development")
========================================================================
This PHP Framework contains the following functionality:
	* Complex URL Routing
	* CouchDB and MySQL Support
========================================================================
Requirements:
	* Tested on apache web server only (others may work, but not tested)
	* AllowOverride set to ON in apache configs
	* Debian Packages: php5 php5-dev libapache2-mod-php5 php5-curl
	  php5-mcrypt php5-suhosin
========================================================================
